these fatal blood clots.

20
00:00:46,647 --> 00:00:48,541
Get to the point. I
have a busy day.

21
00:00:48,565 --> 00:00:50,543
Well, you're familiar with
the company DiaCure?

22
00:00:50,567 --> 00:00:52,396
The biggest dialysis
provider in the country. Yeah.

23
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,397
Yeah. I-I met their
CEO at their annual

24
00:00:54,421 --> 00:00:56,283
shareholders'
meeting last night.

25
00:00:56,307 --> 00:00:59,107
He agreed to give us access
to all their patient records...

26
