on the basis of
your wild hunches.

34
00:01:17,778 --> 00:01:20,256
Take my wild hunch
out of the equation.

35
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:22,714
DiaCure is still an excellent
partner for Chastain,

36
00:01:22,749 --> 00:01:24,950
regardless.

37
00:01:28,905 --> 00:01:31,306
It's Jessica.

38
