00:01:39,866 --> 00:01:41,917
Jessica was waiting
before she was found.

43
00:01:41,952 --> 00:01:44,786
Oh, my God. Jess. Jess!

44
00:01:44,839 --> 00:01:45,982
- Oh, my God.
