Might have fallen
asleep at the wheel.

53
00:02:06,827 --> 00:02:08,321
Oh, my God.

54
00:02:08,345 --> 00:02:11,947
What's her access?
She needs volume now.

55
00:02:11,982 --> 00:02:14,499
One 22-gauge in her
thumb. We're trying

56
