You need to let
us take care of her.

64
00:02:31,317 --> 00:02:33,051
- What?
- You need to let us

65
00:02:33,087 --> 00:02:34,547
take care of her. We got this.

66
00:02:34,571 --> 00:02:37,656
We got it.

67
00:02:37,691 --> 00:02:39,290
No.

68
00:02:39,326 --> 00:02:41,053
- Pravesh,
Pravesh. Pravesh!
- No!

69
00:02:41,077 --> 00:02:42,304
- Whoa, whoa.
- Pravesh, get him out of here!

70
00:02:42,328 --> 00:02:44,157
- Get him out of here now!
- No! Get off of me!

71
00:02:44,181 --> 00:02:46,125
- Go.
- No! Get your hands off of me!

72
00:02:46,149 --> 00:02:49,117
- Wait. Wait.
- Let me stay! I want to stay in the room.

73
00:02:49,152 --> 00:02:50,296
