74
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,497
Now anything?

75
00:02:58,828 --> 00:03:01,413
♪ ♪

76
00:03:17,381 --> 00:03:20,231
- Wait. Wait, wait, wait.
- She's been down too long.

77
00:03:20,266 --> 00:03:22,734
- How much more time?!
- Another 20 seconds.

78
00:03:22,769 --> 00:03:24,697
- Where's
that introducer?
- Happening as fast

79
00:03:24,721 --> 00:03:26,599
- as superhumanly possible.
- Ah.

80
00:03:26,623 --> 00:03:28,389
Come on.

81
00:03:30,027 --> 00:03:33,595
All right, and we... are... in.

82
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:36,064
Get that blood in her now
and add an amp of bicarb.

83
00:03:40,137 --> 00:03:42,087
Two minutes. Pulse check.

84
00:03:45,225 --> 00:03:47,470
I got a pulse. We got a
pulse. All right. All right.

85
00:03:47,494 --> 00:03:49,711
All right. All right.

86
00:03:49,747 --> 00:03:52,125
- It's thready,
but it's there. Jess?
- Okay. All right.

87
00:03:52,149 --> 00:03:53,809
- It's thready, but it's there.
- Here we go.

88
00:03:53,833 --> 00:03:55,116
Jess. Jess, welcome back.

89
00:03:55,152 --> 00:03:56,902
Now stay with me. Stay with me!

90
00:03:56,937 --> 00:03:59,620
Okay, come on. All right.

91
